An ultra-fast, privacy-conscious RAG (Retrieval-Augmented Generation) application built for the 2026 AI ecosystem. This tool allows users to upload PDF documents and engage in a natural language conversation with the content using the high-speed Groq LPU inference engine.

üöÄ Key Features
Near-Instant Responses: Leveraging Groq's LPU technology for sub-second inference.

Local Vectorization: Uses Hugging Face all-MiniLM-L6-v2 for private, cost-free embeddings.

Modular Design: Built with the 2026 standard for LangChain 0.3 modular packages.

Local Persistence: Uses ChromaDB to store your document vectors directly on your machine.

